And so, we... diligently and steadily... continued to solidify
the ground....

\SE\SE[19]Yay, you did it...! \SE[19]Laura of the Zero Moon did
it again! \SE[18]She brought peace to this town...!!
Laura of the Zero Moon...!? That girl...!!

Laura of the Zero Moon...! She possesses both strength and
loveliness, and I have fallen in love...! I will become her oshi
(fan)...!!
